This paper deals with judgment aggregation, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). It also involves game theory (cs.GT) and decision making (cs.DS). The paper proposes a new property for judgment aggregation rules, which falls under the category of mathematical aspects (cs.MA) of computer science.
